{"tid":1624152,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"總括裝修注意事項","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:29:06.000Z","uid":53321,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3443d3711fc1497e683c05dee15e9c6708413d8b","tid":1624152,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"總括琴晚到今朝既討論，睇下大家同唔同意<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 裝修前後必須噴漆寫低罪狀</span></span><br />\neg 奶共、中資<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 針對商鋪宜用水，不宜用火</span></span><br />\n畫面好睇，對附近影響較小<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3.優先針對政府機構、黨鐵等直接危害香港人既地點</span></span><br />\n政府同黨鐵就盡情發揮，商鋪必須慎重考慮，尤其有貴重野就留下手，畫畫噴野玩水就夠<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4.請按比例進裝修</span></span><br />\n詳見：破壞商舖請合乎比例原則<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613194\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613194</a>"},{"pid":"12260a4db9ac0b7aa5f13bcedc4aa92a82c222af","tid":1624152,"uid":53321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"唔係唔做 係到做得好好睇睇"},{"pid":"f911ee754a7aed4f00b5facb1146c1cd2b351b54","tid":1624152,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"政府、黨鐵比起吉野家，罪行重咁多<br />\n冇理由用同等級數裝修吉野家"},{"pid":"6a9ed547ae062b4d8652631586887af07eeffa66","tid":1624152,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:08:01.000Z","msg":"用水對鋪頭影響一樣大，但畫面好睇好多"},{"pid":"0764da4ce0eeba3e533bab0a9ced7d0fc656e49c","tid":1624152,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:08:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5cce985d5738079b02aa7d1af41735f876a9b637","tid":1624152,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"315eec58ee62dccf1b32aae710bbe9044403bf73","tid":1624152,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike"